title: Match History
body: Not sure if its a bug, or if the servers are just taking their time, but a ranked game I just finished isn't showing up on my match history. I was bard, and had full build. Finished just a little before 8am AEST.

replies.body: Thats good to hear ^^ . Shame I wasn't able to do a match review for myself afterwards, but its all good :)

It is possible that this is simply a display issue.  We have also heard reports of the match history in the client taking longer to update than normal.  However, I went ahead and took a look into your account and found your win exactly where you said it would be.  Don't worry, it counted :D
